      "text": [
        " : قُلْتُ لَهُ رَجُلٌ أَوْصَى بِعِشْرِينَ دِينَاراً فِي حَجَّةٍ فَقَالَ «يَحُجُّ بِهَا رَجُلٌ مِنْ حَيْثُ يَبْلُغُهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2927 - Ibn Muskan narrated from Abu Basir, from someone who asked Imam (as):\nI said to him: \"A man instructed in his will to allocate twenty dinars for a Hajj.\"\nImam (as) said: \"A man should perform Hajj with it from wherever the amount suffices for him to begin.\""
        ]
      }
